 README.md | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
index 40b30db..a177d94 100644
--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -49,6 +49,7 @@ are still applicable to the latest code.***
 - Alpine Linux: [`wayback`][alpine-pkg] (in `community` repo)
